Class WaterTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.GameObject

        • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.tiles.WaterTile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WaterTile
extends Tile
    Water will kill any monster, other than the glider, that steps on the tile. When Chip steps on the tile he will be killed unless he is wearing flippers. When a block is pushed on the tile, the block is removed and the tile changes to a dirt tile. If Chip is swimming in the tile when a block is pushed into the tile then Chip will die. If a monster steps on the tile while Chip is swimming in it, the monster will die.
